### Phase 5: HandoffHistory component

**`HandoffHistory.tsx`**

Props: `{ notes: HandoffNote[] }`

Reuse `formatRelativeTime` from `@/lib/autosave` (already exported there).

Layout:
```tsx
<div className={styles.container}>
  {notes.length === 0 ? (
    <p className={styles.emptyText}>No session notes yet</p>
  ) : (
    <ul role="list" className={styles.list}>
      {notes.map(note => (
        <li key={note.id} role="listitem" className={styles.item}>
          <span className={styles.time}>{formatRelativeTime(new Date(note.createdAt).getTime())}</span>
          {note.sceneTitle && <span className={styles.scene}>{note.sceneTitle}</span>}
          {note.whatChanged && <p className={styles.noteValue}>Changed: {note.whatChanged}</p>}
          {note.whatIsNext  && <p className={styles.noteValue}>Next: {note.whatIsNext}</p>}
          <hr className={styles.divider} />
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  )}
</div>
```

