```

`handleSubmitComment(alias, body, anchorIdx)`:
- Validate: alias non-empty, body non-empty; else setSubmitError
- `addComment(storyId, { storyId, token, readerAlias: alias, body, anchor: anchorIdx !== null ? { paragraphIndex: anchorIdx, paragraphPreview: getAnchorPreview(paragraphs, anchorIdx) } : null })`
- Reload comments: `setComments(getComments(id).filter(c => c.token === token))`
- `setCommentBody('')` + inline success indicator

