### Phase 4: CommentThread component

**`CommentThread.tsx`**

Props:
```ts
interface Props {
  comments: FeedbackComment[];
  isWriterView: boolean;
  onSubmit: ((alias: string, body: string) => void) | null;  // null = no form
  onResolve?: (id: string) => void;
  onReopen?: (id: string) => void;
  onToggleFollowUp?: (id: string) => void;
  alias: string;
  onAliasChange: (alias: string) => void;
}
```

Layout:
- Existing comments: alias + timestamp + body + resolve/follow-up buttons (writer view only)
- New comment form (when `onSubmit` provided):
  - `<input placeholder="Your name (alias)" ...>` — shown when no alias yet
  - `<textarea placeholder="Add a comment…" ...>`
  - `<button>Submit</button>` + optional error text

```tsx
<div className={styles.thread}>
  {comments.map(c => (
    <div key={c.id} className={`${styles.comment} ${c.resolved ? styles.resolved : ''}`}>
      <div className={styles.commentMeta}>
