## Risks and mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Paragraph index shifts when story content edited | `paragraphPreview` stored at comment time; display shows original context even if text changed — "Anchored: '…'" remains readable |
| Preview route within AppShell exposes internal nav | Banner clearly labeled "Read-only Preview"; no write actions available; acceptable v1 |
| `getShareLinkByToken` scans all stories — O(stories × links) | Stories capped by practical usage (<100 stories), each with max 5 links; acceptable v1 |
| `navigator.clipboard` unavailable on HTTP localhost | Wrap in try/catch with fallback `window.prompt('Copy this URL:', url)` |
| Multiple share links per story — UI can get long | Show max 3 active links with "Create share link" disabled when at limit |

## Rollback strategy

All additive. Remove "Sharing" and "Feedback" sidebar sections from story page JSX. Preview route is a new file — delete to remove. No data migrations.

## Observability

- No console.log in new code
- Future: instrument `share_link_created`, `comment_submitted`, `comment_resolved` events

